Package fr.uga.pddl4j.parser Description

This package contains the classes of the pddl parser. The parser accepts only PDDL3.0 language. See BNF Description of PDDL3.0 - Alfonso Gerevini and Derek Long for more details. This code is automatically generated with javacc 4.0.
